  Source:
    ID: ce3f70aa-4448-4cfd-a1b7-4a32eb5e8df0
    Title: I Ching
Title: Leadership
---
People’s progress results from union around a central figure. The true
leader fortifies his sublimity, strength, and perseverance. The hesitant
will follow gradually, but the late comers will be left out.
